Dobro.

00:30:32.800 --> 00:30:37.430
Pričekajte trenutak
prije nego što izađete.

00:30:37.889 --> 00:30:39.889
Dobro?

00:30:39.974 --> 00:30:41.974
Dobro? -Dobro.

00:31:19.389 --> 00:31:22.141
